{"type":null,"faqId":45331,"title":"荣耀盒子M321的多屏互动是什么功能，有什么用？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;color:red;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<a name=\"_ZH-CN_TOPIC_0009996548\"></a><span class=\"s1\">热线回复：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>多屏互动是将手机（平板）和电视机的屏幕，通过专门的连接设备（荣耀盒子M321）实现连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>通过荣耀盒子M321的多屏互动功能，您可以将手机、平板、电脑等设备上的多媒体文件通过荣耀盒子M321在电视机上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>荣耀盒子M321支持三种多屏互动方式：华为多屏互动（基于 DLNA 协议，华为做了特别优化）、无线显示（即 Miracast）、DLNA。推荐使用华为多屏互动，使用更流畅。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>盒子兼容苹果的 Airplay。当苹果设备与盒子连接至同一网络。苹果设备上会出现</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164848\" style=\"width:0.30208334in;height:0.32291666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>。在播放苹果设备的视频、音乐、图片时，您可以点击</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=164849\" style=\"width:0.30208334in;height:0.32291666in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>，推送到电视上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">互联网\\电商等其他非热线回复：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>多屏互动是将手机（平板）和电视机的屏幕，通过专门的连接设备（荣耀盒子M321）实现连接。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>通过荣耀盒子M321的多屏互动功能，您可以将手机、平板、电脑等设备上的多媒体文件通过荣耀盒子M321在电视机上播放。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span>荣耀盒子M321支持三种多屏互动方式：华为多屏互动（基于 DLNA 协议，华为做了特别优化）、无线显示（即 Miracast）、DLNA。推荐使用华为多屏互动，使用更流畅。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":245,"faqType":"多屏互动","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"852","faqTypeCode":"Media_Device-Screen-Sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442556874000,"seriesProductName":"MediaQ M321,MediaQ M321-20","visitedTimes":40,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"多屏互动,荣耀盒子","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}